  "time_ut": 1660722997,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0dd4\u0db4\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2 \u0db6\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dd4\u0da9\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc5\u0dd2 \u0da2\u0dd0\u0d9a\u0dbd\u0dd3\u0db1\u0dca \u0d9a\u0db4\u0dca\u0db4\u0db8\u0dca \u0db1\u0da9\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dda \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dca\u0dad\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Super Bollywood actress Jacqueline is the defendant in the extortion case",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Indian media reports that Sri Lankan super Bollywood actress Jacqueline Fernandez has been named as a defendant in the money laundering case filed against Sukesh Chandrashekhar by the Indian Financial Intelligence Unit for extorting an amount of 215 crore Indian rupees.",
        "The Financial Intelligence Unit has started an investigation into Sukesh Chandrashekhar's ex-Ranbaxy promoter Mr. Shivendra Singh's bail by deceiving his wife, Mrs. Aditi Singh, and obtaining nearly INR 215 crores.",
        "Jacqueline Fernandez was given gifts of 5.71 crore Indian rupees from the money obtained and due to the close friendship between Mr. Sukesh Chandrashekar and Mrs. Jacqueline Fernandez, the officers of the Financial Intelligence Unit questioned Jacqueline Fernandez for more than 5 hours in August last year.",
        "Indian media said that Jacqueline Fernandez revealed during the questioning that she recognized Chandrashekar through Sukesh Chandrashekar's wife Lena Paul and that Sukesh Chandrashekar also cheated her.",
        "The Indian media reported that the officers of the Indian Financial Intelligence Unit have made Mrs. Fernandez a defendant in the case of Mr. Sukesh Chandrashekhar, alleging that Jacqueline Fernandez knew that Mr. Sukesh Chandrashekhar would give her gifts from the fraudulently obtained money."
      ],
